            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">üö´ Government Censorship</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li><strong>China:</strong> Great Firewall blocks Google, Facebook, Twitter, Wikipedia, and 10,000+ sites</li>
              <li><strong>Russia:</strong> Blocks opposition news, VPN services, and social media during protests</li>
              <li><strong>Turkey:</strong> Blocks Wikipedia, Twitter (during crises), and independent news sites</li>
              <li><strong>Iran:</strong> Heavily censors internet, blocks messaging apps during unrest</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">üì∫ Streaming Geo-Restrictions</h3>
