        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The advertising industry has built a $600 billion surveillance infrastructure to track you across websites, apps, and devices. It's not just creepy‚Äîit's invasive.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How Advertisers Track You</h3>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">üç™</span>
              <div>
