            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-2xl">üõí</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Data Broker Profiles</h4>
                <p>Companies like Acxiom and Experian buy and sell detailed profiles including income, health conditions, political views, and purchase history.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-600 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">‚úÖ How a VPN Reduces Tracking (Partially)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            VPNs hide your IP address, which is one tracking method. However, cookies and fingerprinting still work. For maximum privacy, combine a VPN with:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside ml-4">
            <li>Privacy-focused browser (Firefox, Brave)</li>
