          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            For personal privacy, use a consumer VPN like <a href="/reviews/mullvad" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Mullvad</a> or <a href="/reviews/protonvpn" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">ProtonVPN</a> for non-work browsing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="who-needs" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Who Should Use a VPN? (Spoiler: Everyone)</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          VPNs aren't just for hackers and activists. Here's who benefits from VPN protection:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
